headline: Clorox to Present at 2026 Citi Global Consumer & Retail Conference
summary: The Clorox Company (NYSE: CLX) today announced that Chief Financial Officer Luc Bellet will participate in a fireside chat at the Citi Global Consumer & Retail Conference in Miami, Florida, on Monday, Mar. 9. A live webcast of the presentation will begin at 8:45 a.m. ET (5:45 a.m. PT) and can be accessed on the company's website. A replay of the webcast will be available following the event.

headline: Blue Shield of California Appoints Veteran Finance Leader Kevin Jacobsen to Board of Directors
summary: Blue Shield of California today announced the appointment of Kevin Jacobsen, former Chief Financial Officer (CFO) of The Clorox Company, to the nonprofit health plan's Board of Directors. Jacobsen brings more than three decades of financial and operational leadership experience across global organizations.
